IPMI 	- Intelligent Platform Management Interface
IPMB	- Intelligent Platform Management Bus
PET 	- Platform Event Trap
SMI	- System Management Interface
BMC	- Baseboard Management Controller
SMBUS	- System Management Bus
PMBUS	- Power Management Bus
DRAC	- Dell Remote Access Card - Dell's IPMI implementation
iLO	- integrated Lights Out - HP ISS IPMI implementation
SDHC	- Secure Digital High Capacity flash memory - 32 GB limit
SDXC	- Secure Digital eXtended Capacity flash memory - 2TB limit
OF	- Open Firmware used by Sun, Apple, IBM ppc, etc.

